ab7d-127c590bd2dc" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/03633280-82dd-11ee-ab7d-127c590bd2dc" style="height:388px;width:620px;" alt="将促销版 Z790 EVA 英雄版与已售版本进行比较的图片，其中有一个有趣的拼写错误。" data-uuid="42513357-9c15-3e57-8f9b-f04394d710ac"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">华硕</div></figure></a><p>华硕提醒我们所有人，为什么必须仔细检查您的工作，以防出现错误。 <a data-i13n="cpos:26;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/asus-revealed-to-be-total-anime-fan-poseur-via-costly-typo-on-motherboard-034417256.html"><ins>它推出了一系列主板，以满足热门动漫系列</ins><em><ins>《新世纪福音战士》</ins></em>粉丝的需求</a>。但印刷错误意味着这些单位的名称改为“EVANGENLION”，这可能使它们比以前更适合收藏。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:27;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/asus-revealed-to-be-total-anime-fan-poseur-via-costly-typo-on-motherboard-034417256.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-sony-whiffs-another-gaming-handheld-121546041.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-sony-whiffs-another-gaming-handheld-121546041.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 2f9dd59a-f879-4da0-9736-700427f7c290</guid><dc:creator>丹尼尔·库珀</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 12:15:46 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1699960024</ingested><modified> 2023-11-14T11:07:09+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Daniel Cooper]]></category><media:content height="1464" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/4f320c00-82dc-11ee-bcf9-c5e0175a1947" width="2500"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html>